ADDRGOTO
--------

@{b}NOM@{ub}
     AddrGoto -- Change the current entry in the address book.

@{b}SYNTAXE@{ub}
     ALIAS/A

@{b}FONCTION@{ub}
     Makes the named alias the current entry in the address book.
     The address book window is redrawn to make the new current entry
     visible.

@{b}ENTREES@{ub}
     alias   - alias of the entry to turn into the current one

@{b}RESULTAT@{ub}
     RC est réglé à 5 si l'alias donné n'a pas été trouvé.

@{b}NOTES@{ub}

@{b}EXEMPLE@{ub}

@{b}BUGS@{ub}

@{b}VOIR AUSSI@{ub}

