     <STEM>VALUE - info returned by the query

@{b}NOTES@{ub}
     Superseded by @{" USERINFO " link "RX_USERINFO"} in V2.0+.  Don't use it in new scripts.

@{b}EXEMPLE@{ub}
         /* Enable result codes */

         OPTIONS RESULTS

         /* Request info */

         GETCONFIGINFO NAME VAR name
         GETCONFIGINFO EMAIL VAR email

         /* Display results */

         SAY 'User name:    'name
         SAY 'User address: 'email

@{b}BUGS@{ub}
